# 🚀 Using Jetty Instead of Tomcat

Remove Tomcat:

```xml
<exclusion>
    <groupId>
        org.springframework.boot
    </groupId>
    <artifactId>
        spring-boot-starter-tomcat
    </artifactId>
</exclusion>
```

Add Jetty:

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>
        org.springframework.boot
    </groupId>
    <artifactId>
        spring-boot-starter-jetty
    </artifactId>
</dependency>
```

---

# 🚀 Using Undertow

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>
        org.springframework.boot
    </groupId>
    <artifactId>
        spring-boot-starter-undertow
    </artifactId>
</dependency>
```

Undertow is known for:

* High Performance
* Low Memory Usage
* Asynchronous Processing

---

# 📊 Tomcat vs Jetty vs Undertow

| Feature           | Tomcat   | Jetty     | Undertow  |
| ----------------- | -------- | --------- | --------- |
| Default           | ✅        | ❌         | ❌         |
| Performance       | Good     | Very Good | Excellent |
| Lightweight       | Moderate | Yes       | Yes       |
| Community Support | Large    | Good      | Good      |

