# ⚙ Useful Server Properties

## Change Context Path

```properties
server.servlet.context-path=/api
```

URL:

```text
http://localhost:8080/api
```

---

## Change Port

```properties
server.port=8081
```

---

## Enable Compression

```properties
server.compression.enabled=true
```

---

## Set Session Timeout

```properties
server.servlet.session.timeout=30m
```

