# ⭐ Advantages of Embedded Server

* No External Installation
* Easy Deployment
* Standalone Application
* Faster Development
* Portable
* Easy Testing

---

# ❌ Limitations

* Slightly Higher Memory Usage
* Less Flexible than Dedicated Servers
* Large Enterprise Systems may use External Servers

