# 📝 Summary

* Embedded Server is a built-in web server.
* Spring Boot uses Embedded Tomcat by default.
* Jetty and Undertow are supported alternatives.
* Default server port is 8080.
* Server settings can be changed using `application.properties`.
* Embedded servers make Spring Boot applications standalone and easy to deploy.

